Fourth Department,

October, 1960

(October 20, 1960) In the Matter of Delaware, Lackawanna and Western Railroad Company, Respondent, v. Winfield S. Long et al., as Assessors of the Town of Erwin, Appellants. 1958 Assessment.

Order unanimously affirmed, with $25 costs and disbursements. (Appeal from order of Steuben Special Term denying motion by respondents to dismiss the petition.) Present — Bastow, J. P., Goldman, Halpern, MeClusky and Henry, JJ.
